Get to know your coach

I’m Sayed Salem, Certified Personal Trainer, level 4 Strength & Conditioning Coach, Rehab specialist and Sports Nutritionist, from Egypt and resident in UAE.

I’ve been working as a Personal Trainer since 2017 and still counting, i helped 100+ people to get the best version of themselves and to get better lifestyles to be a productive person in life.

I’m here to Teach you how to know more about your Body and to teach you more about Nutrition and how your body works.

I’m here to support and help you get the best version of yourself to be a productive person in your family and to have the best life ever.
